50:14.160 --> 50:17.520
my advice is stop overthinking a good situation.

50:17.520 --> 50:20.160
An enviable woman wanted to be with you.

50:20.160 --> 50:24.160
So sit back, relax, and enjoy the clout.

50:24.720 --> 50:27.040
